更純粹的因果<br />\n就好似你掟位蘋果落地 個蘋果就會跌落地咁<br />\n呢個例子係容易想像甚至見得到因果"},{"pid":"6ee7a130c6b46c846622e14f18c0055da8b57bcc","tid":2187013,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"128b5924a22fa4dca1cea36b092d04a609f03267","tid":2187013,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2de68c6be87d16a8d071cad97e60f4dcdbf7fe83","tid":2187013,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be34b154aa113f6c1ca71d02d0df04e3fd645141","tid":2187013,"uid":317305,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:11:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功後會清算佢哋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:05:48.000Z","msg":"因果就係啊Q精神<br />\n<br />\n就算尼采都有講，死後壞人受刑係弱者嘅幻想，「奴隸道德」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"有冇本書睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbc1d45bbab890bb07e91169bac59e093844606","tid":2187013,"uid":269044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b210bbcf79af08aa8d3064e831c92d3dc8ea8b8","tid":2187013,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba233df4824641fb797aa11d30bb02aae9449e69","tid":2187013,"uid":269044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72f2f00acc9b543985a3d9f9783844736542bc49","tid":2187013,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"假設一個超有錢既人，有錢到李嘉誠咁，但佢日日整尻啲窮人，派飯比窮人食就實落幾包瀉藥落去整尻窮人。或者好睇唔起窮人，一見到就會被說話佢聽，你覺得佢有生之年會唔會仆街？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"因果關係，我自己睇就係你掉個橙上天係因個橙跌返落地係果，咁再細分個果的話咪個橙可能比人跳高接左或其他結果囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:44:25.000Z","msg":"跌返落地係地心吸力？同埋你見到晒，因果循環正路應該見唔到架下話，所以做唔到反應。但你個橙跌落嚟，你見到打中你個頭，你仲唔縮？應該唔算係因果下話，只係普通物理現象"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:20:58.000Z","msg":"所以我講細分個果為個橙可能比人跳高接住左式其他野，咁呢個係其中一個你估唔到既果，其實冇話見唔見到，我以最簡單黎解構我覺得既因果，假設有人殺左人，佢既果係比人拉去坐監，呢個係第一個果，兇手潛逃左呢個係第二個因，之後變成通緝犯呢個係第二個果，咁佢可以做更多既野去加大個惡果，潛逃攪到冇哂朋友家人呢個都係果，所以果係咪一定睇唔到呢？未必，只係我地唔察覺姐<br />\n<br />\n以上係我自己睇法姐<br />\n<br />\n可能講得1999"},{"pid":"1930d89432a2c6b17cb56b1471795e4b8ebb93c0","tid":2187013,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ee7a130c6b46c846622e14f18c0055da8b57bcc","tid":2187013,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"128b5924a22fa4dca1cea36b092d04a609f03267","tid":2187013,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2de68c6be87d16a8d071cad97e60f4dcdbf7fe83","tid":2187013,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功後會清算佢哋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:05:48.000Z","msg":"因果就係啊Q精神<br />\n<br />\n就算尼采都有講，死後壞人受刑係弱者嘅幻想，「奴隸道德」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"有冇本書睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"Genealogy of the Morality"},{"pid":"fb1222d62458f04e19f6a0ce7fe512bfcc54c426","tid":2187013,"uid":363701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be34b154aa113f6c1ca71d02d0df04e3fd645141","tid":2187013,"uid":317305,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:11:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:21:59.000Z","msg":"可能唔係報係佢地身上 係屋企人身上呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁係唔係仲慘？"},{"pid":"0078d925d408243aae33142c9